# 🌾 Smarthub Agrochain — Project Overview

## What Is This Project?

**Smarthub Agrochain** is a **B2B agricultural marketplace web application** built as a frontend demo. Its purpose is to connect **international buyers** with **African farmers** who supply premium agricultural commodities — such as cashew nuts, cocoa beans, spices, grains, and fresh produce — through a transparent, traceable digital platform.

Think of it as a **digital trading hub for African agro-exports**, with dashboards, order tracking, wallets, and a product marketplace — all built as a polished, production-style frontend (currently with mock/simulated data, no live backend yet).

---

## Tech Stack

| Technology | Version | Role |
|---|---|---|
| **Next.js** | 16 | App Router, SSR, page routing |
| **React** | 19 | UI component rendering |
| **TypeScript** | 5 | Type safety across all files |
| **Tailwind CSS** | 4 | Utility-first styling |
| **Framer Motion** | 12 | Smooth page & component animations |
| **Recharts** | 3 | Charts & data visualisation (dashboard) |
| **Lucide React** | Latest | Icon library |
| **clsx + tailwind-merge** | Latest | Conditional CSS class utilities |

> **Deployed on:** Vercel (zero-config Next.js deployment)

---

## High-Level Architecture

```
Browser (User)
    │
    ▼
Next.js App Router (src/app/)
    │
    ├── Pages (routes) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
    │   ├── / (Home)            → Landing page                                   │
    │   ├── /about              → About the platform                             │
    │   ├── /contact            → Contact form page                              │
    │   ├── /login              → Buyer/Farmer sign-in                           │
    │   ├── /signup             → Buyer/Farmer registration                      │
    │   ├── /cart               → Shopping cart page                             │
    │   └── /dashboard          → Protected area with sub-pages:                 │
    │       ├── /dashboard/orders     → Order management                         │
    │       ├── /dashboard/products   → Product listings                         │
    │       ├── /dashboard/tracking   → Shipment tracking                        │
    │       ├── /dashboard/wallet     → Wallet & financials                      │
    │       ├── /dashboard/settings   → Account settings                         │
    │       └── /dashboard/notifications → Notifications                         │
    │                                                                            │
    ├── React Context (Global State) ─────────────────────────────────────────── │
    │   ├── CartContext     → Cart items, add/remove, localStorage sync          │
    │   ├── UserContext     → Auth state, user profile, localStorage sync        │
    │   └── SearchContext   → Product search query state                         │
    │                                                                            │
    ├── Components ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── │
    │   ├── layout/         → Navbar, Footer (global wrappers)                   │
    │   ├── ui/             → Reusable UI primitives (Button, Input, Toast…)     │
    │   ├── dashboard/      → Dashboard-specific components                      │
    │   └── cart/           → Cart-specific components                           │
    │                                                                            │
    └── lib/ ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── │
        ├── data/products.ts  → Static mock product catalogue                    │
        ├── constants.ts      → App-wide constants                               │
        └── utils.ts          → cn() helper for merging Tailwind classes         │
```

---

## Folder-by-Folder Breakdown

### `src/app/` — Pages & Routing
The core of the Next.js **App Router**. Every folder here becomes a URL route.

| Folder/File | URL Route | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `page.tsx` | `/` | Homepage / landing page |
| `layout.tsx` | (all pages) | Root layout — wraps ALL pages with Navbar, Footer, Context Providers |
| `template.tsx` | (all pages) | Page transition animation wrapper |
| `globals.css` | — | Global CSS resets and base styles |
| `about/` | `/about` | About page |
| `contact/` | `/contact` | Contact page |
| `login/` | `/login` | Login page |
| `signup/` | `/signup` | Signup page |
| `cart/` | `/cart` | Cart page |
| `dashboard/` | `/dashboard` | Dashboard area (with its own nested layout) |

---

### `src/app/dashboard/` — Dashboard Sub-Pages
The dashboard has its **own nested layout** (`dashboard/layout.tsx`) that adds a Sidebar and Header on top of every dashboard page.

| Folder | URL | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `page.tsx` | `/dashboard` | Main dashboard (stats, charts, recent offers) |
| `orders/` | `/dashboard/orders` | Order list & management |
| `products/` | `/dashboard/products` | Product catalogue management |
| `tracking/` | `/dashboard/tracking` | Shipment/logistics tracking |
| `wallet/` | `/dashboard/wallet` | Wallet balance, transactions |
| `settings/` | `/dashboard/settings` | Account & notification settings |
| `notifications/` | `/dashboard/notifications` | Notification centre |

---

### `src/components/` — UI Components

#### `layout/` — Global Layout
- **`Navbar.tsx`** — Top navigation bar (logo, links, auth buttons, cart icon)
- **`Footer.tsx`** — Site-wide footer

#### `ui/` — Reusable UI Primitives
| Component | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `Button.tsx` | Styled button variants (primary, secondary, outline, etc.) |
| `Input.tsx` | Styled text input field |
| `Select.tsx` | Styled dropdown select |
| `Switch.tsx` | Toggle switch (used in settings) |
| `Toast.tsx` | Global toast/notification popup system |
| `Hero.tsx` | Landing page hero section |
| `Connectivity.tsx` | Section showing platform connectivity/supply chain |
| `TargetMarket.tsx` | Section displaying target market segments (buyers, importers, processors) |
| `Testimonials.tsx` | Testimonials/reviews carousel section |

#### `dashboard/` — Dashboard Components
| Component | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `Header.tsx` | Dashboard top bar (search, notifications, profile) |
| `Sidebar.tsx` | Left navigation sidebar for dashboard routes |
| `StatsCards.tsx` | KPI stat cards (revenue, orders, etc.) |
| `RevenueChart.tsx` | Recharts-powered revenue line/bar chart |
| `RecentOffers.tsx` | Table of recent trade offers |
| `notifications/` | Notification list components |
| `orders/` | Order table & detail components |
| `tracking/` | Map + shipment tracking UI |
| `wallet/` | Wallet balance cards + transaction history |

#### `cart/` — Cart Components
- Components specific to the shopping cart page

---

### `src/context/` — Global State (React Context)

| File | What It Manages |
|---|---|
| `CartContext.tsx` | Cart items, quantity, add/remove/clear — persisted in `localStorage` |
| `UserContext.tsx` | Logged-in user info, auth state — persisted in `localStorage` |
| `SearchContext.tsx` | Product search query string — shared across components |

> All three contexts are provided at the **root layout** level so every page can access them.

---

### `src/lib/` — Utilities & Data

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `data/products.ts` | Static mock product catalogue (name, price, origin, category, images, etc.) |
| `constants.ts` | App-wide constants (e.g., site name, nav links) |
| `utils.ts` | `cn()` function — merges Tailwind class names safely using `clsx` + `tailwind-merge` |

---

### `src/types/` — TypeScript Types

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `index.ts` | Shared TypeScript interfaces and types (e.g., `Product`, `Order`, `User`, `CartItem`) used across the whole app |

---

### `public/` — Static Assets

All images are stored here and referenced directly:
- **`LOGO.jpg`** — The Smarthub Agrochain brand logo
- **`hero-bg.jpg`** — Landing page hero background
- **`avatar-1.png` to `avatar-5.png`** — Testimonial profile pictures
- **`agrochain-farmers.png`**, **`agrochain-logistics.png`** — Feature/section imagery
- **`target-buyer.png`**, **`target-importer.png`**, **`target-processor.png`** — Target market segment images
- **`vegetable-container*.png`** — Product visuals
- **`brush-border.svg`** — Decorative SVG border graphic
- `images/` and `logos/` — Additional image assets

---

### `scripts/` — Utility Scripts

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `generate_brush.js` | Script to programmatically generate the brush-border SVG graphic |
| `process_brush.py` | Python script for post-processing the brush SVG |

---

### Root Config Files

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `package.json` | Project metadata, scripts (`dev`, `build`, `start`, `lint`), dependencies |
| `next.config.ts` | Next.js configuration (image domains, etc.) |
| `tsconfig.json` | TypeScript compiler configuration |
| `eslint.config.mjs` | ESLint linting rules |
| `postcss.config.mjs` | PostCSS config (required by Tailwind CSS 4) |
| `.gitignore` | Files excluded from Git (node_modules, .env, build artifacts, etc.) |
| `.vercelignore` | Files excluded from Vercel deployment |
| `build.log` | Build output log (likely from a previous build run) |

