## Known Limitations (Demo Build)

> [!WARNING]
> This is currently a **frontend demo only** — no real backend exists.

- **Authentication** is fake — no real login verification. User data stored in `localStorage`.
- **Products** are hardcoded static data in `lib/data/products.ts`.
- **Cart** only persists in browser `localStorage`, not a database.
- **Orders, Tracking, Wallet** all display mock/dummy data.
- **No real payments** — no Stripe, Paystack, or any payment processing.

